	<title>Confirm_for_booking_id_65468798</title>
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.10.2.min.js"></script>
	<link href="https://netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
	<script src="https://netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row">
			<!-- BEGIN INVOICE -->
			<div class="col-xs-12">
				<div class="grid invoice">
					<div class="grid-body">
						<div class="invoice-title">
							<div class="row">
								<div class="col-xs-6">
									<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/ae/CASA_logo.svg" alt=""
										height="35" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
									<h2>Booking Confirmation<br>
										<span class=" small">orderId #<%= order.id %></span>
									</h2>
									<p>Please present either an electronic or paper copy of your booking confirmation
										upon
										check-in.</p>
								</div>
								<div class="col-xs-6 text-right">
									<!-- <img src="https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?data=HelloWorld&amp;size=200x200"
										alt="" title="" />
									<br> -->
								</div>
							</div>

						</div>
						<hr>
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-xs-6" style="margin-bottom: 20px">
								<div>
									<strong>Customer's Name:</strong>
									<%= order.Guest.fullname %> <br>
										<strong>Lead guest:</strong>Claudion<br>
										<strong>Occupancy:</strong>Claudion<br>
										<strong>Benefits:</strong>Claudion<br>
										<strong>Special request:</strong>Claudion<br>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="col-xs-6 text-right">
								<div style="background-color: rgb(221,221,221); padding: 2px 8px; height: 140px;">
									<strong>Email:</strong>
									<%= order.Guest.email %><br>
										<strong>Tel:</strong>
										<%= order.Guest.phone %><br>
											<strong>Payment Method:</strong>
											<%= order.paymentMethod %> <br>
												<strong>Payment Date:</strong>
												<%= order.date %> <br>
													<strong>Promotion:</strong> nothing <br>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class=" row">
							<div class="col-md-12">
								<p style="background-color: rgb(221,221,221); padding: 2px 8px;">Cancellation
									Policy:
									Free Cancellation is free any time before check-in date. If you
									do not check in or cancel by then, no refund will be given by property.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="col-md-12">
								<p style="background-color: rgb(221,221,221); padding: 2px 8px;">Benefits
									Included:
									Parking, Free WiFi, Express check-in, Drinking water</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-md-12">
								<h3>ORDER SUMMARY</h3>
								<table class="table table-striped">
									<thead>
										<tr class="line">
											<% if(admin){ %>
												<td class="text-center"><strong>RoomID</strong></td>
												<% }%>

													<td class="text-center"><strong>Check-In</strong></td>
													<td class="text-center"><strong>Check-Out</strong></td>
													<td class="text-center"><strong>Price</strong></td>
													<td class="text-right"><strong>SUBTOTAL</strong></td>
										</tr>
									</thead>
									<tbody>
										<tr>
											<% if(admin){ %>
												<td class="text-center">
													<%= order.RoomInOrders.RoomId%>
												</td>
												<% }%>
													<td class="text-center">
														<%= order.RoomInOrders.from %>
													</td>
													<td class="text-center">
														<%= order.RoomInOrders.to %>
													</td>
													<td class="text-center">$<%= order.RoomInOrders.Room.price %>
													</td>
													<td class="text-right">$<%= order.RoomInOrders.Room.price %>
													</td>
										</tr>
										<tr>
											<% if(admin){ %>
												<td colspan="3"></td>
												<% } else{%>
													<td colspan="2"></td>
													<% } %>
														<td class="text-right"><strong>Taxes</strong></td>
														<td class="text-right"><strong>0</strong></td>
										</tr>
										<tr>
											<% if(admin){ %>
												<td colspan="3"></td>
												<% } else{%>
													<td colspan="2"></td>
													<% } %>
														<td class="text-right"><strong>Total</strong></td>
														<td class="text-right"><strong>$<%= order.total %></strong></td>
										</tr>
									</tbody>
								</table>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-md-12 text-right identity">
								<p>Designer identity<br><strong>Crit Dang</strong></p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-md-12 text-left identity">
								<img src="https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?data=HelloWorld&amp;size=200x200"
									alt="" title="" style="display: block;
									margin-left: auto;
									margin-right: auto;
									width: 50%;" />
								<br>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-md-12 text-left identity " style="border:2px solid #dddddd;">
								<ul>
									<li><span style="color: red;">Important notice:</span> to protect your
										personal data and payment
										information,
										never disclose your personal data or payment information or transfer
										funds to any person calling or messaging you from unofficial
										communication channels outside of Agodaâ€™s platform. If you have received
										such communications, please report any suspicious or fraudulent activity
										by contacting our customer support and always check with us if you are
										unsure before responding to external or suspicious communications
										(calls, emails, text messages, etc.)</li>
									<li><span style="color: red;">IMPORTANT:</span> At check-in, you must
										present a valid photo ID with your
										address confirming the same name as the lead guest on the booking. For
										bookings paid with a credit card, you may also need to present the card
										used to make the payment. Failure to do so may result in the hotel
										requesting additional payment or your reservation not being honored.
									</li>
									<li>All rooms are guaranteed on the day of arrival. In the case of a
										no-show, your room(s) will be released and you will be subject to the
										terms and conditions of the Cancellation/No-Show Policy specified at the
										time you made the booking as well as noted in the Confirmation Email.
									</li>
									<li>The total price for this booking does not include mini-bar items,
										telephone usage, laundry service, etc. The property will bill you
										directly.
									</li>
									<li>In cases where Breakfast is included with the room rate, please note
										that
										certain properties may charge extra for children travelling with their
										parents. If applicable, the property will bill you directly. Upon
										arrival, if you have any questions, please verify with the property.
									</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<!-- END INVOICE -->
		</div>
	</div>

	<style type="text/css">
		body {
			margin-top: 20px;
			background: #eee;
		}

		.invoice {
			padding: 30px;
		}

		.invoice h2 {
			margin-top: 0px;
			line-height: 0.8em;
		}

		.invoice .small {
			font-weight: 300;
		}

		.invoice hr {
			margin-top: 10px;
			border-color: #ddd;
		}

		.invoice .table tr.line {
			border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
		}

		.invoice .table td {
			border: none;
		}

		.invoice .identity {
			margin-top: 10px;
			font-size: 1.1em;
			font-weight: 300;
		}

		.invoice .identity strong {
			font-weight: 600;
		}


		.grid {
			position: relative;
			width: 100%;
			background: #fff;
			color: #666666;
			border-radius: 2px;
			margin-bottom: 25px;
			box-shadow: 0px 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		}
	</style>

	<script type="text/javascript">

	</script>
</body>

</html>